00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:44,860
 Dakle, jednu mirnu povorku

503
00:35:44,860 --> 00:35:45,760
 radosnih ljudi.

504
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:49,280
 I to su svi mediji prenijeli

505
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:51,140
