549
00:36:57,020 --> 00:36:57,760
 To nije jedno...

550
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,600
 Pa ne samo crkvu.

551
00:36:58,600 --> 00:36:59,160
 To je...

552
00:36:59,160 --> 00:36:59,720
 Ma naravno.

553
00:36:59,720 --> 00:37:01,080
 On želi reći da

554
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:03,580
 ti, ako si ti komičar,

555
00:37:03,580 --> 00:37:05,020
 ako si ti urednik...

556
00:37:05,020 --> 00:37:05,720
 Da, nemam ja što.

557
00:37:05,720 --> 00:37:06,740
 Ti nemaš što.

558
00:37:06,740 --> 00:37:08,040
 ili kako bi trebao

559
00:37:08,040 --> 00:37:08,900
 doma zaboraviti

560
00:37:08,900 --> 00:37:09,520
