573
00:37:22,680 --> 00:37:23,460
 Prema crkvi,

574
00:37:23,460 --> 00:37:24,680
 prema nama samima.

575
00:37:24,680 --> 00:37:26,580
 Pa nekad i zbog toga

576
00:37:26,580 --> 00:37:27,120
 imate problema.

577
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:27,680
 Pa nekad,

