00:37:40,420 --> 00:37:42,300
 on zahtjeva i inteligenciju

589
00:37:42,300 --> 00:37:44,300
 i mjeru

590
00:37:44,300 --> 00:37:47,360
 i ako želi biti konstruktivan.

591
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:47,760
 Dakle,

592
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:49,940
 humor je iznimno moćan.

593
00:37:49,940 --> 00:37:50,260
 On je,

594
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:52,520
 humor je u nekim,

595
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:53,700
