596
00:37:53,700 --> 00:37:56,580
 ismijavanjem neke važne ideje

597
00:37:56,580 --> 00:37:57,680
 ljude u propasti.

598
00:37:57,680 --> 00:37:57,940
 Dakle,

599
00:37:57,940 --> 00:38:00,420
 humor je moćna stvar.

600
00:38:00,420 --> 00:38:00,900
 Dakle,

601
00:38:00,900 --> 00:38:01,720
 ovisi osobi,

602
00:38:01,720 --> 00:38:03,340
 ovisi onome kako se osoba,

603
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:05,060
 kako se osoba služi humorom.

604
00:38:05,060 --> 00:38:05,480
 Humor je,

605
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:08,040
 nije sam po sebi odmah dobar.

606
