623
00:38:27,560 --> 00:38:29,140
 Kaže Fulton Sheen,

624
00:38:29,140 --> 00:38:30,060
 humor je kad spojiš

625
00:38:30,060 --> 00:38:31,160
 dvine spojive ideje.

626
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,940
 To je ono što je u temelju humoru.

627
00:38:32,940 --> 00:38:34,700
 I onda te to čini da se smiješ.

628
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:36,380
 I sad to možeš na razne načine.

629
00:38:36,380 --> 00:38:37,960
 Gagom možeš,

630
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:40,360
 spojiš dvije ideje

631
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:41,080
 i tako.

632
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:43,500
 Možeš i tako da vrijeđaš,

633
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:45,140
 pa spojiš dvine spojive ideje

634
00:38:45,140 --> 00:38:45,500
 i tako.

635
00:38:45,500 --> 00:38:46,300
 Evo mi smo izabrali

636
00:38:46,300 --> 00:38:47,060
