637
00:38:47,060 --> 00:38:48,500
 Tako, da govorite

638
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:49,100
 o pojavama,

639
00:38:49,100 --> 00:38:49,540
 ne o ljudima.

640
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:50,120
 O pojavama,

641
00:38:50,120 --> 00:38:50,520
