667
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:22,440
 Znate što me jednom

668
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:23,260
 baš opustilo

669
00:39:23,260 --> 00:39:24,100
 u tom smislu

670
00:39:24,100 --> 00:39:25,560
 da nastavimo

