 za abortus.

719
00:40:20,180 --> 00:40:20,900
 Sjeo je.

720
00:40:20,900 --> 00:40:22,200
 Možda ga potakne

721
00:40:22,200 --> 00:40:23,080
 na neki način time.

722
00:40:23,080 --> 00:40:23,820
 Evo, dakle,

723
00:40:23,820 --> 00:40:24,800
 to razlikovanje.

724
00:40:24,940 --> 00:40:28,620
 Nema alternative u konačnici

725
00:40:28,620 --> 00:40:30,320
 komunikaciji.

726
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:30,760
 Nema je.

