744
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:05,840
 da će ga mediji zbog toga napaditi

745
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:07,520
 i onda jedan dio ljudi

746
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:09,440
 ne usude se biti ono što jesu.

747
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:10,380
 I to je problem.

748
00:41:10,380 --> 00:41:11,860
 To je sve sad istina.

